    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "914684_4_636-724",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "636-724",
      "markText": "我躺在树荫下的童车中，夏日煦愉，天空蔚蓝；金晖闪耀，绿叶婆娑；车篷掀起，我正好美滋滋地醒来，觉得通体舒泰，妙不可言。我看着阳光闪烁，树叶憧憧，花枝幢幢。一切奇异至极，斑斓美妙。",
      "totalCount": 816,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=914684&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=636&rangeEnd=724",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1d7325005df4fc1d739c07b?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=636&rangeEnd=724"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "914684_3_418-476",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "418-476",
      "markText": "我的一生，是潜意识自我实现的故事。潜意识中的一切都想成为卓然之事，连人格也想脱离潜意识状况而发展，觉得自己是个整体。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=914684&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=418&rangeEnd=476",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1d7325005df4fc1d739c07b?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=418&rangeEnd=476"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "914684_4_2446-2478",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2446-2478",
      "markText": "这些事证明我有无意识的自杀冲动，或表明我毁灭性地抗拒现世的生活。",
      "totalCount": 624,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=914684&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2446&rangeEnd=2478",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1d7325005df4fc1d739c07b?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2446&rangeEnd=2478"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "914684_3_1322-1381",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1322-1381",
      "markText": "我总觉得人生如同从根茎上长出来的植物，其本真的生命隐而不现，蕴蓄于根茎中。沃土上可见者只维持一夏。然后枯萎，昙花一现。",
      "totalCount": 408,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=914684&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1322&rangeEnd=1381",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1d7325005df4fc1d739c07b?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1322&rangeEnd=1381"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "914684_3_1705-1783",
